0 ARTISTEAL~

Syntax: artisteal <character> <item>

This command allows you to steal one artifact from a player of
ANY status.   This allows you to retrieve artifacts from players
outside your status range.  The artifact is transferred directly
to your inventory, instead of being left on their corpse as is
the case with decapitation.

