0 QUERY NUKEBUF~
As you may know, if you enter a lot of commands (i.e. spamming
berserk, etc), they get put into a buffer.  Well, I've just
created a way to work with that buffer.  These two new commands
are not real commands, and you must fully type them, and ! does
not work.  But they do not care if you have other commands
waiting, or if you have a wait state.  Query will list all of
the commands you have buffered, and Nukebuf will clear them.
If you are not clear on what this does, just spam berserk alot,
then immediately type query.  You will see a list of berserks.
Type nukebuf, then type query again, and they are all gone.

Coded by Devik Kyrn, eternal warrior
~

